content.content: Customizing your theme is as simple as creating a few CSS variables. The color palette now uses more vibrant wide gamut colors without you needing to understand what any of that even means.

content.content: Using grid utilities directly in your HTML makes it so much easier to reason about complex layouts. Transitions that work the way you'd expect — throw a few utilities on an element and you're in business. transition duration-750linear

content.content: Tailwind uses CSS layers so you don’t have to worry about specificity issues. Supporting multiple language text directions is no longer a nightmare. Tag an element as a container to let children adapt to changes in its size.

content.title: Redefining real-time performance
content.content: No need to remember that complicated gradient syntax — create silky-smooth gradients with just a few utility classes. Our next-generation rendering engine delivers unmatched speed and efficiency, empowering creators to push boundaries like never before. Sometimes two dimensions aren’t enough. Scale, rotate, and translate any element in 3D space to add a touch of depth.
